Hjortstam &amp; Ryvarden, Mycotaxon 15: 271. 1982. ≡ 
<taxonomicName class="Agaricomycetes" family="Thelephoraceae" genus="Odontia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Fungi" lsidName="Odontia polycystidifera" order="Thelephorales" pageId="13" pageNumber="78" phylum="Basidiomycota" rank="species" species="polycystidifera">Odontia polycystidifera</taxonomicName>
